= Opinion Polls
  
We can host an opinion polls to foresee the results in the following election

- @host
- @return: We cant or choose not to host a poll at the moment.
  
@host
title: Host a poll
subtitle: -1 resource
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
choose-if: resources >= 1
on-arrival: resources -= 1

If elections are held now.

<span style="color: #000000;"><b>CS</b></span>: ([+ cs_votes +] + [+ random +])%

<span style="color: #D00000;"><b>SDAPÖ</b></span>: ([+ sdapo_votes +] + [+ random +])%

[? if npo_formed : <span style="color: #002050;">NPÖ</span> ([+ npo_votes +] + [+ random +])% ?]

